                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13114SaqawaD"><roleName type="title">አባ፡</roleName> 
                                        ፀቃውዓ፡ ድንግል፡</persName> ወልደ፡ 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8554sardaPe"><roleName type="title">አባ፡</roleName> ሰርፀ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡</persName> ዘወሀቦ፡ 
